The paper deals with multimodal question answering using personal photo albums, which involves computer vision (CV) and natural language processing (NLP) techniques. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) and cs.CL (Computation and Language) are the most likely sub-categories. Additionally, the paper involves multimedia (cs.MM), information retrieval (cs.IR), and machine learning (cs.LG) techniques, which are also relevant to the task.
